OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FBritain must "move away" from its
OL,7,Freliance on the United States for
OL,8,Fdefence and security, MPs and peers
OL,9,Fhave warned amid continued
OL,10,Ftransatlantic tensions.
OL,12,FIn a report published on Friday,
OL,13,FParliament's Joint Committee on the
OL,14,FNational Security Strategy (JCNSS)
OL,15,Fsaid the UK should continue to
OL,16,Fcollaborate with the US "where
OL,17,Fpractical".
OL,26,@nD@NOUnD@XO]xD@YOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
