PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774627872
OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FBut it warned the Government should
OL,7,Fprepare for a "worst-case scenario" in
OL,8,Fwhich Europe could no longer rely on
OL,9,FUS support in a crisis.
OL,11,FInstead, the JCNSS said the UK should
OL,12,Fplan to transition to a more European-
OL,13,Fled Nato and "move away from a
OL,14,Fbilateral relationship with the United
OL,15,FStates that is so dependent on the
OL,16,Flatter".
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@cO]uD@NOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
