PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774627872
OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FBritain currently relies on US support
OL,7,Fin several key national security
OL,8,Fareas, including maintenance of its
OL,9,FTrident nuclear missiles, intelligence
OL,10,Fsharing and major projects such as the
OL,11,FF35 fighter jet and Aukus submarine
OL,12,Fdeal with Australia.
OL,14,FBut the JCNSS said recent comments by
OL,15,FUS president Donald Trump had shown
OL,16,F"demonstrable areas of tension" in UK-
OL,17,FUS relations that could "compromise
OL,18,Fthe reliability of these dependencies".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@_O]yD@YOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
