OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774627872
OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FAs well as his wider criticism of the
OL,7,FNato alliance and threats to annex
OL,8,FGreenland earlier in the year, Mr
OL,9,FTrump has repeatedly criticised the
OL,10,Fdeal to transfer sovereignty of the
OL,11,FChagos Islands to Mauritius and been
OL,12,Fwilling to use tariffs against
OL,13,Ftraditional allies.
OL,15,FJCNSS chairman and Labour MP Matt
OL,16,FWestern said: "The unpredictability of
OL,17,Fthe US relationship is a growing
OL,18,Fconcern.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
