PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774627872
OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,F"The UK's deep dependence on the US
OL,7,Ffor security guarantees has a long
OL,8,Fhistory, and the partnership will
OL,9,Foutlast prime ministers and presidents
OL,10,Falike.
OL,12,F"But the UK needs a clear plan to move
OL,13,Faway from some areas of strategic
OL,14,Freliance to ensure the UK can pursue
OL,15,Fits national interest."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
