OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774627872
OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FAs well as creating a more European-
OL,7,Ffocused Nato, the committee
OL,8,Frecommended the Government pursue
OL,9,Fstronger relations with "middle
OL,10,Fpowers" such as Australia, India and
OL,11,FCanada.
OL,13,FThe recommendation follows a speech by
OL,14,FCanadian Prime Minister Mark Carney at
OL,15,FDavos in January, in which he called
OL,16,Ffor "middle powers" to work together
OL,17,Fin the face of "an era of great power
OL,18,Frivalry".
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@GO]xD@EOUxD@SO]yD@POUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
