PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774627872
OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FNaomi Smith, chief executive of
OL,7,Fcampaign group Best for Britain, said
OL,8,Fthe JCNSS was "completely right".
OL,10,FShe said: "With a tyrant on Europe's
OL,11,Fdoorstep, we must urgently move away
OL,12,Ffrom a dangerous overreliance on US
OL,13,Fdefence infrastructure and stand
OL,14,Fshoulder to shoulder with our closest
OL,15,Fallies and friends."
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@`O]rD@KOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
