OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"National security is our first duty.
OL,8,FWe've wasted no time hardening and
OL,9,Fsharpening our approach to keeping the
OL,10,Fcountry safe, delivering the biggest
OL,11,Fsustained investment in defence since
OL,12,Fthe Cold War.
OL,14,F"All this work is strengthened by our
OL,15,Fcooperation with allies around the
OL,16,Fworld as leading members of Nato and
OL,17,Fthe Five Eyes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
