OL,3,CBritain must 'move away' from defence
OL,4,Creliance on America, MPs and peers warn
OL,6,F"On China, our approach is consistent
OL,7,F` we will co-operate where we can and
OL,8,Fchallenge where we must. That means
OL,9,Ftackling the threats posed by China
OL,10,Fbut also pursuing and maximising the
OL,11,Fopportunities it creates. "
